Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:19.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:21.60,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:24.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我才要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:33.06,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.04,0:21:47.24,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,奈奈同学？
